```
@startuml xinsongyan_talos_pal_locomotion_slmc
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F7F7F7
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Operator" as Operator

package "TALOS Robot Locomotion Controller" {
  rectangle "ROS Node\n(Main Controller)" as MainController
  rectangle "WBC Plugins" as WBC
  rectangle "DCM Controller" as DCM
  rectangle "State Estimator" as StateEstimator
  rectangle "Safety Layer" as Safety
  rectangle "Simulation Environment" as Simulation
  rectangle "Real Robot" as RealRobot
}

package "Configuration Files" {
  rectangle "YAML Configs" as YAML
}

Operator --> MainController : Initiates Control

MainController --> WBC : Loads Plugins via pluginlib
MainController --> DCM : Generates Trajectories
MainController --> StateEstimator : Receives Feedback
MainController --> Safety : Monitors State

MainController --> Simulation : Simulated Execution
MainController --> RealRobot : Real-world Execution

MainController --> YAML : Loads Parameters
YAML --> WBC
YAML --> DCM
YAML --> StateEstimator
YAML --> Safety

Safety --> MainController : Alerts/Adjustments
@enduml
```